{"tid":2159174,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"點睇王詩安、安安？","createTime":"2020-08-16T07:09:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T18:48:43.000Z","uid":53619,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4630904edc5658f8faf395597887e7b82fc62362","tid":2159174,"uid":53619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:09:05.000Z","msg":"2013年 早熟<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xnYRxKV1ZM0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxnYRxKV1ZM0&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJKf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=83c49944\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xnYRxKV1ZM0</a><br />\n2014年 愛存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Qu1ZTCEw6wg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQu1ZTCEw6wg&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJKf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=d408b13b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Qu1ZTCEw6wg</a><br />\n2016年 I Don't Know、Home、Heartbeat<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZxuFuVS3zfI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZxuFuVS3zfI&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJKf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=021a4a93\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZxuFuVS3zfI</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mrEee4bhc7Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmrEee4bhc7Y&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJKf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=9a33fa60\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mrEee4bhc7Y</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mM93eJ4BayQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmM93eJ4BayQ&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJKf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=9a6cc2b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mM93eJ4BayQ</a><br />\n<br />\n2017年去咗方大同嗰邊發展曲風唔同哂，有特色咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2017年 一步成詩、明天、徠卡味，呢一年嘅曲都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iE-buimT8KQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiE-buimT8KQ&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJKf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=19b7e6ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iE-buimT8KQ</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/U60_PkV47b0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FU60_PkV47b0&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJKf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=3182d950\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/U60_PkV47b0</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PFux-Lfu2Vk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPFux-Lfu2Vk&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJKf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=dd5fe673\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PFux-Lfu2Vk</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年 Random Day<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8fImSv504W0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8fImSv504W0&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJKf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=d8972227\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8fImSv504W0</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年 脈絡、Hello, I said<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/G92g7aMkEcI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FG92g7aMkEcI&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJKf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=970178df\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/G92g7aMkEcI</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-LyCbzSEs-4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-LyCbzSEs-4&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJKf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=52af52c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-LyCbzSEs-4</a><br />\n<br />\n唱Live一樣唱得無咩大失準跟MV差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要挑剔嘅地方就係有時會唱到唔夠氣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過佢啲歌難唱到癡線，超多高音起伏位<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UMuMg4DHveg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUMuMg4DHveg&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJKf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=c35327cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UMuMg4DHveg</a><br />\n縱然寶馬雕車飄香滿路 路上可有你<br />\n只怕永遠都會懷疑 我走在何夕 你卻在何地<br />\n有人走過七步成他的詩 願我一步有我的你<br />\n呢幾句咁難唱都唱得咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c4112a5e23c3b4677534524f967cac5c0e699a7","tid":2159174,"uid":40979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:13:24.000Z","msg":"同佢老細一樣好有才華<br />\n愛因斯坦，徠卡味，一步成詩，月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72fc9b3d2e5a52f789b95b2070dd722f7ae1c0d6","tid":2159174,"uid":25075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:16:46.000Z","msg":"初<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f51dbd9fd89e45fb33c9ef0d3dea0526f65d0a1","tid":2159174,"uid":312417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72fc9b3d2e5a52f789b95b2070dd722f7ae1c0d6","tid":2159174,"uid":25075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:16:46.000Z","msg":"初<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:59:19.000Z","msg":"識貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢個人同宜家啲音樂都好有氣質<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持佢同佢個fd孫盛希"},{"pid":"898e6fdeed1f8b189b428b3e07c3be33d807aaf7","tid":2159174,"uid":53619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:07:42.000Z","msg":"方大同跟王詩安是咪有路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"678b7d5b0236646b40d8d7ae7b74352d98c99a06","tid":2159174,"uid":53619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:25:05.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"14b9a371e6d91f262209a1d9cee4c0ea9cc768ee","tid":2159174,"uid":53619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:04:38.000Z","msg":"2020年詩安仲出唔出專輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80d8d5ad8ac332716bc3618b55e66f34cafee71","tid":2159174,"uid":53619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci